Subject: [PATCH AUTOSEL 5.3 143/203] ASoC: fsl_ssi: Fix clock control issue in master mode
Date:   Sun, 22 Sep 2019 14:42:49 -0400
Message-Id: <20190922184350.30563-143-sashal@kernel.org>
